README for mbrback


OVERVIEW
========

mbrback creates a backup of your hard driveâ€™s MBR and its partition table. 
You can then use mbrback to restore the MBR boot code, full MBR, or 
partition table from the backup files.

Homepage & Instructions:
    http://igurublog.wordpress.com/downloads/script-mbrback/

Downloads:
    https://github.com/IgnorantGuru/mbrback/tags
    https://github.com/IgnorantGuru/mbrback/tree/master/packages

Bug Reports:
    https://github.com/IgnorantGuru/mbrback/issues


INSTALLATION
============

To install:

    wget https://github.com/IgnorantGuru/mbrback/raw/master/mbrback
    sudo install mbrback /usr/local/bin/mbrback

To remove:
    
    sudo rm /usr/local/bin/mbrback


